reviewText: Love Amazon and there efficient deliveries. I really enjoy the According to Jim Series.

Although I have only watched through Season 2 so far, every character in this sitcom is marvelous in their own way.  The writing is often hilarious and the situations so well-suited to the characters.  I particularly like the way the relationship between Belushi and Williams-Paisley is fleshed out without being a charicature.

They're a hilarious bunch, especially when I watch it with my husband and we pick apart the characters, pointing out which characteristic of Cheryl or Jim that I or he possess.

But why don't they have subtitles!! I would like the option!
I wish tat the shows on tv were still this good. You simply can't go wrong with according to Jim. Worth every penny
We bought this set for my dad for Christmas -it's one of his favorite shows and he is really enjoying it
